<D>__{mayday. mayday. mayday. to any vessel. this is arctic warrior. arctic warrior. arctic warrior. whiskey alpha sierra bravo four zero niner two. last known position one seven four west, five seven north. i am afloat and drifting. require immediate medical assistance for one person, possibly comatose. i am a one hundred twenty foot civilian tug, hove to at port bow of disabled passenger liner chimera. i repeat, chimera. over.}
